### List newsfeed categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/newsfeeds/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### List newsfeed categories, with filters
# Filters:
# - filter[search]     string  Search by category title
# - filter[published]  int     0=unpublished, 1=published, 2=archived, -2=trashed
# - filter[language]   string  Language code or "*"
# - filter[level]      int     Category nesting level
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/newsfeeds/categories?filter[published]=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### Get newsfeed category data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/newsfeeds/categories/5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### Create newsfeed category
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/newsfeeds/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"title": "Test Newsfeed Category",
	"alias": "test-newsfeed-category",
	"parent_id": 0,
	"published": 1,
	"language": "*"
}

### Update newsfeed category
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/newsfeeds/categories/5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"published": 0
}

### Delete newsfeed category (must be trashed first)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/newsfeeds/categories/5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
